PurchaseOrderSearch is a SearchForm
    Layout
        four column distributed
            Company
            PurchaseOrder
            POCode
            Buyer
        four column distributed
            Vendor
            Vendor.VendorSearchDocument
                label is "VendorKeyword"
            CalculateTotalAmount
                label is "Total"
            DerivedPurchaseOrderStatus
                label is "Status"
        header3 of "ShowMore"
            collapsible
                initially collapsed
                use show more or less affordance
            four column distributed
                PurchaseOrderDate
                    label is "PODate"
                DefaultDeliveryDate
                    label is "DefaultDeliveryDate"
                ShipToLocation
                    label is "ShipTo"
                PurchaseFromLocation
                    select is NonRemitToActivePurchaseFromLocations
            four column distributed
                HasIDMJobError
                IDMJobFailLimitReached
